#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.store_tensor_descriptor"
msgstr "# triton.language.store_tensor_descriptor"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:4
msgid "简介：将数据块存储到张量描述符指定内存位置"
msgstr "Introduction: Store the data block to the memory location specified by the tensor descriptor."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.store_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"    desc: tensor_descriptor_base,\n"
"    offsets: Sequence[constexpr | tensor],\n"
"    value: tensor,\n"
"    _semantic=None\n"
") -> tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specification"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名         | 类型                              | 说明                                                         |\n"
"| ----------- | ------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `desc`      | `tensor_descriptor_base`        | 张量描述符对象，由 `make_tensor_descriptor` 创建，定义了内存布局（形状、步长、块大小等）。 |\n"
"| `offsets`   | `Sequence[constexpr \\| tensor]` | 数据存储的起始偏移量序列，用于指定当前线程块要存储的数据位置                             |\n"
"| `value`     | `tensor`                        | 待写入的张量数据块                                                  |\n"
"| `_semantic` | -                               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"| ----------- | ------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `desc`      | `tensor_descriptor_base`        | Tensor descriptor object, created by `make_tensor_descriptor`, defining the memory layout (shape, strides, block sizes, etc.). |\n"
"| `offsets`   | `Sequence[constexpr \\| tensor]` | Sequence of starting offsets for data storage, used to specify the data location to be stored by the current thread block. |\n"
"| `value`     | `tensor`                        | The tensor data block to be written. |\n"
"| `_semantic` | -                               | Reserved parameter, external calls are not supported for now. |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:14
msgid "返回值：`tensor` - 实际写入的数据块"
msgstr "Return value: `tensor` - the actual written data block"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:20
msgid ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
"|Ascend A2/A3| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
msgstr ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
"|Ascend A2/A3| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:22
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:24
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensors |\n"
"| Ascend | Only supports 1~5D tensors |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:26
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5 dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:30
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:32
msgid "结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint16、uint32、uint64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint16, uint32, and uint64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:34
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:36
msgid "`store_tensor_descriptor` 提供两种调用形式："
msgstr "`store_tensor_descriptor` provides two calling forms:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:38
msgid "* 面向对象方法调用（推荐）"
msgstr "* Object-oriented method invocation (recommended)"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"desc.store(offsets, value)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:42
msgid "* 函数式接口调用"
msgstr "* Functional interface invocation"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:44
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.store_tensor_descriptor(desc, offsets, value)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:46
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 做就地绝对值计算："
msgstr "The following example implements an in-place absolute value calculation on the input tensor `x`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/store_tensor_descriptor.md:48
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def inplace_abs(in_out_ptr, M, N, M_BLOCK: tl.constexpr, N_BLOCK: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 创建张量描述符\n"
"    desc = tl.make_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"        in_out_ptr,\n"
"        shape=[M, N],\n"
"        strides=[N, 1],\n"
"        block_shape=[M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK],\n"
"    )\n"
" # 计算当前线程对应的偏移量\n"
"    moffset = tl.program_id(0) * M_BLOCK\n"
"    noffset = tl.program_id(1) * N_BLOCK\n"
" # 加载数据，计算绝对值，存储结果\n"
"    value = desc.load([moffset, noffset])\n"
"    desc.store([moffset, noffset], tl.abs(value))\n"
"## 初始化张量\n"
"M, N = 256, 256\n"
"x = torch.randn(M, N, device=\"npu\")\n"
"## 配置块大小和网格\n"
"M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK = 32, 32\n"
"grid = (M // M_BLOCK, N // N_BLOCK)\n"
"inplace_abs[grid](x, M, N, M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

